title: Top Places to visit in Mumbai suburban, Bandra(East), Maharashtra
content: Mumbai Suburban District is a district of Maharashtra in Konkan Division. Its headquarters is in Bandra. It consists of three administrative subdivisions : Kurla, Andheri, and Borivali. title: Top Places to visit in Mumbai City, Maharashtra
content: Mumbai City District is a district of Maharashtra in Konkan Division. As a city district, it has no headquarters or subdivisions.
